        <strong style="font-size:0.95rem;">Final Exam Grade Calculator</strong>
        <p style="opacity:0.6;font-size:0.83rem;margin:0.4rem 0 0;line-height:1.4;">Stop guessing what you need to pass. Use this calculator to find the exact score you must get on your final exam to reac...</p>
