        <strong style="font-size:0.95rem;">Final Grade Calculator: What Do You Need to Pass?</strong>
        <p style="opacity:0.6;font-size:0.83rem;margin:0.4rem 0 0;line-height:1.4;">Find out exactly what you need on your final exam to pass your class. Instantly calculate the grades required to reach y...</p>
